Added a test case for falsy prefaults (`false`, `0`, `""`). All 3713 existing tests pass.

Use `Object.create(null)` instead of `{}` for the form data object and replace `key in form` with `Object.hasOwn(form, key)` to prevent `__proto__` keys in FormData from polluting the object prototype chain.

